#: ../../user/changelog.md:7
msgid ""
"`Vi.setTimerTickModeWithInterval` — the `\"interval\"` tick mode now "
"accepts its `interval` (ms) argument."
msgstr ""
"`Vi.setTimerTickModeWithInterval` — `\"interval\"` ティックモードで "
"`interval`（ミリ秒）引数を渡せるようになりました。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:8
msgid ""
"`Vitest.aroundAll` / `Vitest.aroundEach` — Vitest 4 lifecycle wrappers; "
"the callback receives a `runSuite` / `runTest` thunk to await."
msgstr ""
"`Vitest.aroundAll` / `Vitest.aroundEach` — Vitest 4 のライフサイクルラッパー。"
"コールバックは await すべき `runSuite` / `runTest` サンクを受け取ります。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:9
msgid ""
"`Vi.useFakeTimersWith` — install fake timers with explicit "
"`FakeTimerInstallOpts` (`now`, `toFake`, `shouldAdvanceTime`, …)."
msgstr ""
"`Vi.useFakeTimersWith` — `FakeTimerInstallOpts`（`now`、`toFake`、"
"`shouldAdvanceTime`、…）を明示してフェイクタイマーをインストールします。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:10
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"`Vi.waitForWith` / `Vi.waitUntilWith` — `waitFor` / `waitUntil` taking an"
" explicit `{interval?, timeout?}` options record."
msgstr ""
"`Vi.waitForWith` / `Vi.waitUntilWith` — `waitFor` / `waitUntil` に明示的な "
"`{interval?, timeout?}` オプションレコードを渡せます。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:12
msgid "Changed"
msgstr "変更"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:14
msgid ""
"**Breaking:** `onTestFailed` / `onTestFinished` (and their `…Async` "
"variants) callbacks now receive the per-test `testContext` value "
"(`testContext => unit`) instead of taking no argument. Update callbacks "
"from `() => …` to `_ctx => …`."
msgstr ""
"**破壊的変更:** `onTestFailed` / `onTestFinished`（および `…Async` "
"バリアント）のコールバックは、引数なしではなくテスト単位の `testContext` 値（`testContext => "
"unit`）を受け取るようになりました。コールバックを `() => …` から `_ctx => …` に更新してください。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:15
msgid ""
"**Breaking:** `Vi.doMock` now returns a `Vi.disposable` handle (matching "
"Vitest 4) instead of `unit`."
msgstr ""
"**破壊的変更:** `Vi.doMock` は `unit` ではなく（Vitest 4 に合わせて）`Vi.disposable` "
"ハンドルを返すようになりました。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:16
msgid ""
"**Breaking:** Closed-set arguments are now polymorphic variants instead "
"of `string`: `toBeTypeOf` (e.g. `#string`), `spyOnAccessor` (`#get` / "
"`#set`) and `coverage.provider` (`#istanbul` / `#v8` / `#custom`). `pool`"
" and `environment` stay `string` (extensible unions). Update call sites "
"from string literals to variant tags."
msgstr ""
"**破壊的変更:** 閉じた集合の引数が `string` ではなく多相バリアントになりました: "
"`toBeTypeOf`（例: `#string`）、`spyOnAccessor`（`#get` / `#set`）、"
"`coverage.provider`（`#istanbul` / `#v8` / `#custom`）。`pool` と `environment` は"
"（拡張可能な union のため）`string` のままです。呼び出し箇所を文字列リテラルから"
"バリアントタグに更新してください。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:18
msgid "Fixed"
msgstr "修正"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:22
msgid "0.1.0 (2026-06-19)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../user/changelog.md:24
msgid ""
"Initial release: type-safe ReScript bindings covering the Vitest 4 "
"surface."
msgstr "初回リリース: Vitest 4 のサーフェスを網羅した型安全な ReScript バインディング。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:28
msgid ""
"Mock call-argument matchers: `toHaveBeenCalledWith`, "
"`toHaveBeenLastCalledWith`, `toHaveBeenNthCalledWith`, "
"`toHaveBeenCalledExactlyOnceWith` (each with a two-argument `…With2` "
"variant)."
msgstr ""
"モックの呼び出し引数マッチャー: "
"`toHaveBeenCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenLastCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenNthCalledWith`、`toHaveBeenCalledExactlyOnceWith`（それぞれ"
" 2 引数版 `…With2` を含む）。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:29
msgid ""
"Mock return-value matchers: `toHaveReturnedTimes`, `toHaveReturnedWith`, "
"`toHaveLastReturnedWith`, `toHaveNthReturnedWith`."
msgstr ""
"モックの返り値マッチャー: "
"`toHaveReturnedTimes`、`toHaveReturnedWith`、`toHaveLastReturnedWith`、`toHaveNthReturnedWith`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:30
msgid ""
"`Vi.MockFn` lifecycle helpers: `mockResolvedValueOnce`, "
"`mockRejectedValueOnce`, `mockReturnThis`, `getMockName`, `mockName`, "
"`getMockImplementation`, `withImplementation`."
msgstr ""
"`Vi.MockFn` のライフサイクルヘルパー: "
"`mockResolvedValueOnce`、`mockRejectedValueOnce`、`mockReturnThis`、`getMockName`、`mockName`、`getMockImplementation`、`withImplementation`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:31
msgid ""
"`Vi` mock inspection and hoisting helpers: `mocked`, `isMockFunction`, "
"`hoisted`."
msgstr "`Vi` のモック検査・ホイストヘルパー: `mocked`、`isMockFunction`、`hoisted`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:32
msgid ""
"Per-test lifecycle hooks: `onTestFailed`, `onTestFinished` (each with an "
"`…Async` variant)."
msgstr "テスト単位のライフサイクルフック: `onTestFailed`、`onTestFinished`（それぞれ `…Async` バリアントを含む）。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:33
msgid ""
"Type and predicate matchers: `toBeTypeOf`, `toBeInstanceOf`, `toBeOneOf`,"
" `toSatisfy`."
msgstr "型・述語マッチャー: `toBeTypeOf`、`toBeInstanceOf`、`toBeOneOf`、`toSatisfy`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:34
msgid ""
"Async-mock resolve matchers: `toHaveResolved`, `toHaveResolvedTimes`, "
"`toHaveResolvedWith`, `toHaveLastResolvedWith`, `toHaveNthResolvedWith`."
msgstr ""
"async モックの resolve マッチャー: "
"`toHaveResolved`、`toHaveResolvedTimes`、`toHaveResolvedWith`、`toHaveLastResolvedWith`、`toHaveNthResolvedWith`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:35
msgid ""
"Async fake timers: `advanceTimersByTimeAsync`, `runAllTimersAsync`, "
"`runOnlyPendingTimersAsync`, `advanceTimersToNextTimerAsync`, "
"`advanceTimersToNextFrame`."
msgstr ""
"async フェイクタイマー: "
"`advanceTimersByTimeAsync`、`runAllTimersAsync`、`runOnlyPendingTimersAsync`、`advanceTimersToNextTimerAsync`、`advanceTimersToNextFrame`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:36
msgid ""
"Timer inspection: `isFakeTimers`, `getTimerCount`, `getMockedSystemTime`,"
" `getRealSystemTime`."
msgstr ""
"タイマー検査: "
"`isFakeTimers`、`getTimerCount`、`getMockedSystemTime`、`getRealSystemTime`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:37
msgid "Waiting utilities: `waitFor`, `waitUntil`."
msgstr "待機ユーティリティ: `waitFor`、`waitUntil`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:38
msgid "Accessor spies: `spyOnGetter`, `spyOnSetter`."
msgstr "アクセサスパイ: `spyOnGetter`、`spyOnSetter`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:39
msgid ""
"Global and environment stubs: `stubGlobal`, `stubEnv`, "
"`unstubAllGlobals`, `unstubAllEnvs`."
msgstr "グローバル・環境スタブ: `stubGlobal`、`stubEnv`、`unstubAllGlobals`、`unstubAllEnvs`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:40
msgid ""
"Module mocking completion: `importActual`, `importMock`, `doUnmock`, "
"`mockObject`, `dynamicImportSettled`."
msgstr ""
"モジュールモックの補完: "
"`importActual`、`importMock`、`doUnmock`、`mockObject`、`dynamicImportSettled`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:41
msgid ""
"Test modifiers: `testSkipIf`, `testRunIf`, `testFails`, `testFailsAsync`,"
" `testSequential`, `testSequentialAsync`."
msgstr ""
"test 修飾子: "
"`testSkipIf`、`testRunIf`、`testFails`、`testFailsAsync`、`testSequential`、`testSequentialAsync`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:42
msgid ""
"Describe modifiers: `describeTodo`, `describeConcurrent`, "
"`describeSequential`, `describeShuffle`, `describeSkipIf`, "
"`describeRunIf`, `describeFor`."
msgstr ""
"describe 修飾子: "
"`describeTodo`、`describeConcurrent`、`describeSequential`、`describeShuffle`、`describeSkipIf`、`describeRunIf`、`describeFor`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:43
msgid ""
"Asymmetric matchers (`Expect` module): `anything`, `any`, "
"`arrayContaining`, `objectContaining`, `stringContaining`, "
"`stringMatching`, `stringMatchingRegExp`, `closeTo`, "
"`closeToWithPrecision`."
msgstr ""
