"`anything`、`any`、`arrayContaining`、`objectContaining`、`stringContaining`、`stringMatching`、`stringMatchingRegExp`、`closeTo`、`closeToWithPrecision`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:44
msgid "Parameterized test `testFor` (`test.for`)."
msgstr "パラメータ化テスト `testFor`（`test.for`）。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:45
msgid ""
"Assertion guards and special assertions (`Expect` module): `assertions`, "
"`hasAssertions`, `soft`, `poll`, `unreachable`, `unreachableWithMessage`."
msgstr ""
"アサーションガードと特殊アサーション（`Expect` モジュール）: "
"`assertions`、`hasAssertions`、`soft`、`poll`、`unreachable`、`unreachableWithMessage`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:46
msgid "File snapshot matcher: `toMatchFileSnapshot`."
msgstr "ファイルスナップショットマッチャー: `toMatchFileSnapshot`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:47
msgid ""
"Negated asymmetric matchers (`Expect.Not` module): `arrayContaining`, "
"`objectContaining`, `stringContaining`, `stringMatching`, "
"`stringMatchingRegExp`, `closeTo`, `closeToWithPrecision`."
msgstr ""
"否定 asymmetric マッチャー（`Expect.Not` モジュール）: "
"`arrayContaining`、`objectContaining`、`stringContaining`、`stringMatching`、`stringMatchingRegExp`、`closeTo`、`closeToWithPrecision`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:48
msgid ""
"`it` modifiers: `itTodo`, `itConcurrent`, `itEach`, `itFails`, "
"`itSequential`, `itSkipIf`, `itRunIf`."
msgstr ""
"`it` 修飾子: "
"`itTodo`、`itConcurrent`、`itEach`、`itFails`、`itSequential`、`itSkipIf`、`itRunIf`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:49
msgid "Async-body conditional tests: `testSkipIfAsync`, `testRunIfAsync`."
msgstr "async body の条件付きテスト: `testSkipIfAsync`、`testRunIfAsync`。"

#: ../../user/changelog.md:50
msgid "Fake-timer tick mode: `setTimerTickMode`."
msgstr "フェイクタイマーの tick モード: `setTimerTickMode`。"

